ed="T" n="0809a12"/><persName key="A011638">釋慧則</persName>，姓<name>糜</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000010176"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>崑山</placeName></placeName>人也。<date key="j20289602029324" from-iso="+0843-01-01" to-iso="+0843-12-31">九歲</date>，博遊才<lb
ed="T" n="0809a13"/>義，總翫儒經。善種發萌，條然<ptr target="#n485"/>厭俗，以<date from-iso="+0853-02-16" key="j20326592033012" to-iso="+0854-02-04"><name>大中</name><lb
ed="T" n="0809a14"/>七年</date>就京<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName>出家。勤知諷誦，皆如曾<lb
ed="T" n="0809a15"/>習。<date from-iso="+0855-01-26" key="j20333682033751" to-iso="+0856-02-13">九年</date>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042216">本寺</ref>承恩得度。<date from-iso="+0860-01-31" key="j20351992035523" to-iso="+0860-12-20">十四年</date>，棲<persName key="A009180">法寶<roleName>大<lb
ed="T" n="0809a16"/>師</roleName></persName>法席覆講，<date from-iso="+0860-01-31" key="j20351992035523" to-iso="+0860-12-20">當年</date>勅補備員大德。<date from-iso="+0862-02-07" key="j20359372036290" to-iso="+0863-01-26"><name>咸通</name>三年</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809a17"/>就<placeName key="PL000000042269">崇聖寺</placeName>講《俱舍論》<ptr target="#n1429"/>并《喪服儀》<ptr target="#n1865"/>，出《三界圖》<ptr target="#n1866"/>一<lb
ed="T" n="0809a18"/>卷。<date from-iso="+0866-01-25" key="j20373852037768" to-iso="+0867-02-12">七年</date>，於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042216">祖院</ref><ptr target="#n1867"/>代<persName key="A009180">暢<roleName>師</roleName></persName>講。<date from-iso="+0874-01-26" key="j20403082040636" to-iso="+0874-12-20">十五年</date>，勅署臨<lb
ed="T" n="0809a19"/>壇正員。<date from-iso="+0880-02-18" key="j20425222042876" to-iso="+0881-02-06"><name>廣明</name>元年</date>，<persName key="A008599">巢</persName>寇犯闕<ptr target="#n981"/>，<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>俶擾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1048"/>，出<lb
ed="T" n="0809a20"/><placeName key="PL000000043289"><placeName>華州</placeName><placeName>下邽</placeName></placeName>避亂。<date from-iso="+0882-01-27" key="j20432312043614" to-iso="+0883-02-14"><name>中和</name>二年</date>，至<placeName key="PL000000010783">淮南</placeName>，<persName key="A008497">高<roleName>公</roleName>駢</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0809a21"/>召於<placeName key="PL000000010810">法雲寺</placeName>。講罷還<placeName key="PL000000009928">吳</placeName>，刺史<persName key="A011639">楊<roleName>公</roleName></persName>苦留，却<lb
ed="T" n="0809a22"/>遊<placeName key="PL000000014664"><placeName>天台山</placeName><placeName>國清寺</placeName></placeName>挂錫。<date from-iso="+0894-02-14" key="j20476322047985" to-iso="+0895-02-02"><name>乾寧</name>元年</date>至<placeName key="PL000000012309"><placeName>明州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0809a23"/><placeName>育王寺</placeName></placeName>，撰《塔記》一卷，出《集要記》十二卷<ptr target="#n1884"/>。<persName key="A003552"><persName>武肅<lb
ed="T" n="0809a24"/>王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>命於<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>臨壇。以<date key="j20529542052954" when-iso="+0908-09-11"><name>開平</name>二年八月<lb
ed="T" n="0809a25"/>八日</date>示疾坐亡。受生七十四，法臘五十四。<lb
ed="T" n="0809a26"/>窆于<placeName key="PL000000012279">鄮山</placeName>之岡。八戒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g894"/>弟子<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz2"/>刺<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz2"/>史<persName key="A007285">黃晟</persName>營塔。<lb
ed="T" n="0809a27"/><persName key="A011638">則</persName>生常不好<anchor xml:id="beg0809001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>許</sic><corr>訐</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0809001"/>直<ptr type="glossary" target="#g895"/>，以撝謙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g896"/>推人為上。除<lb
ed="T" n="0809a28"/>講貫<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>外，輪誦經呪，自《法華》已降可三四十<lb
ed="T" n="0809a29"/>本，以資口業。覽大藏教兩遍，講鈔<ptr target="#n1290"/>七十遍，<pb ed="T" n="0809b" xml:id="T50.2061.0809b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809b01"/>《俱舍》<ptr target="#n1429"/>、《喪儀》、《論語》各數遍。清苦執持，近<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>苦</sic><corr>古</corr></choice>罕有。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b02"/>入室<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1381"/>弟子<persName key="A010005">希覺</persName>最露鋒頴焉。又<persName key="A011640">元表</persName>者，貞諒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1431"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809b03"/>之士也，言多峭直<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g897"/>，好品藻<ptr type="glossary" target="#g587"/>人事，而高義解<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g544"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b04"/>從習毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>，兼勤外學，書史方術<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g898"/>，無不該覽。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b05"/>早預京師<placeName key="PL000000042216">西明寺</placeName><persName key="A009180">法寶<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>講肆，迨<date notBefore-iso="+0880-02-18" key="j20425222043063" notAfter-iso="+0881-08-12"><name>廣明</name>中</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b06"/><placeName key="PL000000023581">神都</placeName>版蕩，遂出<placeName key="PL000000000197">江表</placeName>，居<placeName key="PL000000013226"><placeName>越州</placeName><placeName>大善寺</placeName></placeName>，講《南<lb
ed="T" n="0809b07"/>山律鈔》。諸郡學人，無不趨集。<persName key="A011640">表</persName>義理縱橫，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b08"/>善其談說，每揮<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>塵</sic><corr>麈</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz3"/>柄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g796"/>，聽者忘疲，號<persName key="A011640">鑑水<lb
ed="T" n="0809b09"/><anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz4"/>闍黎<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz4"/></persName><ptr target="#n1868"/>。著《義記》五卷<ptr target="#n1869"/>，亦號《鑑水》。出門人<persName key="A011641">清福</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b10"/>冠其首焉。</p>
